105
00:08:15,340 --> 00:08:16,890
<b>Magic History, 10 points.</b>

106
00:08:17,180 --> 00:08:19,010
<b>Potions, 3 points.</b>

107
00:08:19,270 --> 00:08:21,100
<b>Magical Mathematics, 10 points.</b>

108
00:08:21,180 --> 00:08:23,480
<b>SHK SHK SHK SHK SHK</b>

109
00:08:23,890 --> 00:08:28,520
<b>He scraped by through the hands-on exams,
