146
00:10:06,210 --> 00:10:08,250
<b>It's not a matter of can or can't!</b>

147
00:10:08,370 --> 00:10:10,250
<b>If you can't, you'll be expelled.</b>

148
00:10:10,250 --> 00:10:12,040
<b>Evil... So brutal...</b>

149
