165
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:30,160
<b>I want to return to the earth like this.</b>

166
00:11:30,290 --> 00:11:31,500
<b>Mash.</b>

167
00:11:33,290 --> 00:11:37,130
<b>I'm sorry, Finn.
Studying is the one thing I can't...</b>

168
00:11:37,920 --> 00:11:39,720
<b>That's not like you, Mash.</b>

169
00:11:42,930 --> 00:11:44,800
<b>The Mash I know</b>

170
