even the most impossible opponents.</b>

171
00:11:48,850 --> 00:11:52,100
<b>I want to graduate together with you.</b>

172
00:11:52,100 --> 00:11:53,730
<b>Together with you, Mash!</b>

173
00:11:56,480 --> 00:11:58,900
