<b>I'll try my best.</b>

178
00:12:17,090 --> 00:12:20,210
<b>What's with all the moles attached to you?</b>

179
00:12:23,840 --> 00:12:25,720
<b>I'm sorry for running away.</b>

180
00:12:25,930 --> 00:12:28,010
<b>Please teach me one more time.</b>

181
00:12:28,260 --> 00:12:31,350
<b>Oh man, what should I do?
I'm not motivated—</b>

182
00:12:31,350 --> 00:12:32,890
<b>Let's try our best, Mash!</b>

183
00:12:32,890 --> 00:12:33,730
