186
00:12:38,900 --> 00:12:40,030
<b>To your seat.</b>

187
00:12:40,570 --> 00:12:41,400
<b>'Kay.</b>

188
00:12:41,400 --> 00:12:43,650
<b>Please don't ignore me.
I'm seriously sorry.</b>

189
00:12:45,160 --> 00:12:49,660
<b><i>And thus, Mash confronted studying,
which he was not so good at.</i></b>

190
00:13:01,340 --> 00:13:03,670
