Graduate with everyone...</b>

195
00:13:28,280 --> 00:13:30,330
<b>Next. Mash Burnedead.</b>

196
00:13:30,620 --> 00:13:32,330
<b>Oh, here.</b>

197
00:13:38,500 --> 00:13:40,340
