praiseworthy, however.</b>

206
00:14:07,150 --> 00:14:08,280
<b>You scraped by!</b>

207
00:14:08,280 --> 00:14:09,620
<b>Just barely.</b>

208
00:14:09,780 --> 00:14:12,990
<b>BAM</b>

209
00:14:11,080 --> 00:14:12,990
<b>Welp, easy peasy.</b>

210
00:14:13,790 --> 00:14:15,330
<b>Don't get cocky.</b>

211
